data.description: Here is your opportunity to own a beautiful move-in ready home in desirable Village Green which is located in the prestigious Methacton School District with NO HOA! It is situated on a large private corner lot and features 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms and is ready to welcome you home. Step inside the front door to find hardwood stairs and floors throughout the main living area. The new neutral décor is throughout the entire home with recessed lighting in the living room and dining room, plus a renovated kitchen with tile floors, backsplash, and pass-through nook to the dining room.  Down the hall is the main bedroom suite with  an attached and fully renovated bathroom with tiled shower. There are two additional well-sized bedrooms also on this level along with a renovated hall bathroom with tub. Located in the hallway is access to the attic for additional storage space. Head downstairs to the lower level and find the 4th bedroom which could also serve as an office for those who need to work from home or an in-law suite. An oversized family room is great for entertaining, especially with an enlarged full bathroom with barn style slider door. A revamped laundry room with cabinetry also features a new heating system; the oil heating was converted to gas in 2022. The laundry room leads out to the garage space which has been semi-finished into additional bonus space, currently being used as a gym, but can still be used as a fully functioning garage if desired. Garage features a brand new garage opener with safety cables installed. Outside you will find a large shed as well as a ride on lawn mower (which is included; as-is) and plenty of space to entertain with a patio in the front of the house as well as a concrete patio on the side for those summer BBQ’s, a professional horseshoe pit,  a fenced yard, and a composite deck off of the living room/dining room through sliding glass doors. All of this in a fabulous location close to shopping and major commuter routes. It looks as good in person (if not better) as it does in the pictures, so put this one on your list and check it out!
